name: ACEInhibitorAllergyintoleranceCodes
title: ACE inhibitor allergy/intolerance codes
description:
Created from RxMix:
Interactive mode with "N0000175562" (Angiotensin Converting Enzyme Inhibitor) as input
1. RxClass: get class members
relaSource: "DAILYMED"
rela: "has_EPC"
direct: 0
term_type: all of "IN", "MIN", and "PIN"
2. filterByProperty
propertyName = RXNAV_HUMAN_DRUG
purpose: (Clinical Focus: Substances that represent ACE inhibitors drugs or the drug class ACE inhibitors),(Data Element Scope: Codes that would be in the reaction.substance field of the FHIR AllergyIntolerance resource),(Inclusion Criteria: Codes at the drug class level and the drug level, including combination medications including an ACE inhibitor),(Exclusion Criteria: None)
